cs.PL, cs.AR, cs.SE, cs.LO, cs.CR 

The paper proposes a static program analysis method for concurrent software, which falls under the category of programming languages (cs.PL) and architecture (cs.AR). The method aims to improve the accuracy of the analysis by considering the memory models of the processors, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also mentions the use of Datalog rules, which is a logic-based approach to solving problems, and is related to logic in computer science (cs.LO) and cryptography and security (cs.CR).
